body:
This PR suggests to use `premix_stage2` modifier to customize validation module input collections instead of `SimGeneral/DataMixingModule/python/customiseForPremixingInput.py` customise function. This transformation will make the introduction of phase2 premixing cleaner.

Tested in CMSSW_10_1_X_2018-03-05-2300 (rebased on top of CMSSW_10_2_X_2018-03-29-2300), no changes expected.

@mdhildreth @kpedro88
